# Database Context Rule

Use these references when modifying models or executing alembic migrations:

- `AI skills/fastapi-database-management.md`
- `AI skills/project-context.md`

## Expected checks

- Never add a password or native authentication logic to user schemas (handled by Traefik).
- Generate and review an Alembic auto-migration after altering `SQLModel` code.
- Depend on SQLite `/app/data/database.db` via `backend/database.py`.
